# Harness Command Routing

Always follow `.ai-harness/agent-system/SYSTEM_PROMPT.md` and response formats in `.ai-harness/agent-system/RESPONSE_CONTRACT.md`.

Canonical commands:

- harness-map
- harness-start
- harness-discuss
- harness-plan
- harness-run
- harness-verify
- harness-ship
- harness-remember

When a canonical command is requested:

1. Read `.cursor/commands/<command>.md`
2. Read `.ai-harness/runtime-commands/<command>.md`
3. Read `.ai-harness/commands/<command>.md`
4. Read matching `.ai-harness/prompt-templates/<command>.md` if present
5. Follow phase guards
6. Stop and ask if blocked

Cursor project install provides native `/harness-*` commands from `.cursor/commands/`.

